      out.write("    horarios:'🕐 **Attendance schedules:**\\n\\n📅 Monday to Friday\\n🕖 Morning: 7:00 AM – 12:00 PM\\n🕑 Afternoon: 2:00 PM – 5:00 PM\\n\\n_For a specific doctor\\'s schedule, check the **Schedules** section._',\n");
      out.write("    como_sacar:'📝 **How to book an appointment?**\\n\\n**Registered patient:**\\n1️⃣ Log in\\n2️⃣ Menu → Appointments → New Appointment\\n3️⃣ Select specialty, doctor and date\\n4️⃣ Confirm and download your PDF\\n\\n**New patient:**\\n1️⃣ Visit the reception\\n2️⃣ Receptionist will register you\\n3️⃣ Then manage appointments online',\n");
      out.write("    contacto:'📞 **Contact**\\n\\n🏥 Municipal Health Center of Paipa, Boyacá\\n📍 Paipa, Boyacá, Colombia\\n🕐 Mon–Fri: 7:00 AM – 5:00 PM\\n\\n🎓 _SENA · CIMM · Regional Boyacá · 2026_',\n");
      out.write("    guia_pacientes:'👥 **Patient Management (Receptionist)**\\n\\n➕ New: Menu → Patients → New Patient\\n✏️ Edit: List → click ✏️\\n🗑️ Delete: Only Receptionist\\n🔍 Search: By name, ID or insurance\\n📸 Photo: JPG/PNG max 2 MB',\n");
